        <detaileddescription>
<para>Called when a progress dialog needs to be displayed</para>
<para>If cancellable (psz_cancel != NULL), you can cancel this dialog by calling <ref refid="group__vlc__dialog__impl_1ga62300f7faf9aefbd5ad8abfa796cdcce" kindref="member">vlc_dialog_id_dismiss()</ref></para>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>to receive this callback, <ref refid="group__vlc__dialog_1ga41302d6e505ed5c80a76666cb8758bc9" kindref="member">vlc_dialog_cbs.pf_cancel</ref> and <ref refid="group__vlc__dialog_1gac6362fc282bdd107a18c31c54b50cb09" kindref="member">vlc_dialog_cbs.pf_update_progress</ref> should not be NULL.</para>
</simplesect>
<parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>p_data</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
